Package: eigencore
Title: Certified Partial Spectral Computation
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bradley", "Buchsbaum", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com")
  )
Author: Bradley Buchsbaum [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Bradley Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Description: Native-oriented foundations for certified partial eigenvalue and
    singular-value computation in R. The package provides native solver paths
    plus operator, problem, planner, result, and certificate APIs for large
    dense, sparse, generalized, and matrix-free spectral problems.
